events:
Chaitra Shukla Paksha starts from 22nd March and ends on 6th of April,
Vaisakha Krishna Paksha starts from 7th April and ends on 20th April.
Panchak Starts on 15th April and ends on 19th of April
Vaishakh Shukla Paksha starts from 21st April and ends on 5th May
Panchak starts on 12th May and ends on 17th May
Vaishakh Shukla Paksha starts from 21st April to 5th of May
Zyeth Shukla Paksha starts from 20th May to 4th June.
Zyeth Krishna Paksha starts from 6th May and ends on 19th May
Panchak starts on 9th June and ends on 13th June
Zyeth Shukla Paksha starts from 20th May to 4th of June
Aashaad Krishna Paksha starts from 5th June to 18th June.
Aashaad Shukla Paksha starts from 19th June and ends on 3rd July
